metadata.name: The Queen
metadata.description:
Title: Queen
Year: 2021
Series: Interior Leather
Photography/Digital Manipulation/ 3D
3264x4928
Model: @alejo_cane

Director:
-Lights please, a throne for this being.
You tell your model:
-Come sit on your throne, look at me and tell me who it is!
The model tells you something
Director: Yes, be yourself!
Perfect!
Post production phase
The director composes the sensuality of his muse with lights, icons and many other details to create a cyborg: a human, a machine, in short, a jumble of possibilities, a not distant future.
